  "body": "### Description\nCheck through the REST API handlers and ensure they handle uint64 overflow problems. In particular anything that accepts an epoch as input and converts it to a slot needs to handle the overflow when the epoch is UInt64.MAX_VALUE (or anything where epoch * slots > MAX_VALUE).\n\n",
